{"tid":1563733,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"世紀飯局！美斯允C朗食餐飯！","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:53:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":155,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"b69a50266e6353bae0f54e2b01e91139b85ad208","tid":1563733,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】過去十年，稱金球獎為美斯與C朗的專屬戰場絕不為過。但C朗就說自己很希望與這位好敵手共晉一次晚餐。<br />\n<br />\n基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）早前接受訪問時，談到與美斯（Lionel Messi）亦敵亦友的關係：「不能否認，美斯令我成為更好的球員，相對亦然。當我取得錦標時一定會令他不快，在我而言亦是一樣。這是好對手的關係，而且並不少見，米高佐敦都有宿敵，F1賽車有冼拿及普羅斯特。他們都有共通點，都是良性的競爭對手。所以我與美斯的關係當然很好，雖然我們未試過共晉晚餐，但希望未來可以。」<br />\n<br />\n聽到C朗的「邀請」之後，美斯似乎都識英雄重英雄：「我會去，沒問題的。我從來都說跟他沒有心病，我們雖然不是至交好友，可能因為從未共事過吧，但我總是在頒獎禮見到他。最近一次頒獎禮我們甚至有過一次長談。我未知一餐晚飯是否可行，始終我們都有自己的生活、自己的工作。但我絕對會答應他的邀請。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"cdce0dadcc58edd61055e04f64e7c5ab72254f56","tid":1563733,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:34:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"248195f2f0f83b40e1a91e054390741cdf0f64ca","tid":1563733,"uid":16659,"like":198,"dislike":1,"score":197,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/NGxkH